This is my second map, its a remake of furex_glassworld from Cs 1.6.
I have made some changes to the design, now when you fall threw the glass you end up in the centre of the room were you can Awp or deagle from but you can be shot as well, there is no way out. I may add some new features in my next version of this map.

*Update*
Added Guns room
Fixed Ct buyzone
Water is buggy
